description: Demolition of existing buildings. Erection of buildings up to 8-storeys high plus basement to provide 152 flats (including 38 Affordable units), 2,228sq.m. of commercial accommodation for retail, food and drink, business and community uses (Class A1, A2, A3, B1, D1) with associated parking, private amenity space and public realm with access through the site.
